What Is Ralei Shell?

Ralei Shell is a powerful command-line shell written in PHP, designed to assist developers and sysadmins in managing and executing various tasks. It provides an interactive environment for PHP scripting, allowing you to run PHP code, execute system commands, and perform file operations directly from the command line. With Ralei Shell, you can easily navigate through directories, manipulate files and directories, and interact with databases, all using the familiar syntax of PHP. Whether you a PHP developer or a system administrator, Ralei Shell offers a convenient and efficient way to work with PHP in a command-line interface.

Author: Rahman Ralei | Version: 1.0
